data.description: Fully furnished, 2413 square foot rustic log home in the beautiful Texas Hill Country! This home offers an open living area, along with 3 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms and a loft space. Enjoy summer evenings outside on the front porch taking in the views. The home sits on 1.6 acres sprinkled with beautiful oak trees and has subdivision access to the sparkling waters of the Frio River. Two storage sheds in the backyard offer extra space for lawn equipment or tinkering in your spare time. The home is move-in ready and waiting for you to make it your own. The kitchen is equipped with stainless steel appliances. With Garner State Park just 10 minutes away and 20 minutes from Concan, this area offers plenty of fun activities such as summer dances, swimming, hiking and fishing. Schedule your private tour today!
